口述实录 | 刑满释放后，我报名了县里抗疫一线，但没想到......。
After serving my sentence, I signed up for the county fight against plague, but didn't expect...
高 集  沈 林。
Gao Ji Shen Lin.
新民周刊                      。
Xinmin Weekly.
